sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Activities List Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open activities list
    UI->>LW: Initial request
    LW->>DB: Query activities (paged, sorted)
    DB-->>LW: Paginated activities
    LW-->>UI: Render table and filters

    User->>UI: Search/filter/sort/paginate
    UI->>LW: Update bound properties
    LW->>DB: Re-query with conditions
    DB-->>LW: Updated paginated result
    LW-->>UI: Re-render list

    User->>UI: Reset filters
    UI->>LW: clear()
    LW-->>UI: Reset state and reload list

    User->>UI: Change language
    UI->>LW: changeLanguage(lang)
    LW-->>UI: Re-render in selected locale
